<h3 class="section-heading">ğŸ§ª Practice: Filename Globbing</h3>

<pre><code>$ mkdir glob
$ cd glob
$ touch alfa bravo charlie delta echo able baker cast dog easy

$ ls              # Show all files
$ ls a*           # Starts with "a"
$ ls *a*          # Contains "a"
$ ls [ac]*        # Starts with "a" or "c"
$ ls ????         # Exactly 4 characters
$ ls ?????        # Exactly 5 characters
</code></pre>

